        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-29" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Pré-condições" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="280" x="210" y="-150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-30" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Pos-condições" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="280" x="210" y="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critérios de Aceitação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="280" x="210" y="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Media&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O utilizador encontra-se devidamente autenticado no sistema com perfil de Atleta ou Encarregado de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Educação.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A equipa técnica ou o sistema (através de registos de jogos/provas) já inseriu dados de métricas, notas&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;qualitativas ou resultados associados a este atleta em específico.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="1260" x="491" y="-150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema agrega os dados históricos da base de dados e gera uma visualização estruturada (tabelas ou&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;gráficos) que reflete a evolução do atleta.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A interface devolve a informação estritamente em modo de apenas leitura (&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;76&quot;&gt;read-only&lt;/i&gt;) para este ator.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="1260" x="490" y="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. A interface deve permitir filtrar o histórico de desempenho por época desportiva, competição ou&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;modalidade.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. Os dados quantitativos (ex: golos, tempos, pontuações) devem ser apresentados preferencialmente com&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;recurso a elementos visuais (ex: gráficos de linhas ou de barras) para facilitar a perceção da evolução.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O sistema deve garantir a privacidade total dos dados, impossibilitando de forma estrita que um atleta&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;aceda aos relatórios de desempenho individual de outros colegas.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="1260" x="490" y="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
